00:17:22,145 --> 00:17:24,274
<font color="#ffff54">I'd feel safe pissing again.</font>

287
00:17:31,511 --> 00:17:33,501
<font color="#ffff54">Line up. State your names.</font>

288
00:17:31,819 --> 00:17:33,402
