<font color="#ffff54">Maeda, sir.</font>

290
00:17:37,819 --> 00:17:39,402
我是前田

291
00:17:40,144 --> 00:17:41,610
<font color="#ffff54">Ohno, sir.</font>

292
00:17:40,444 --> 00:17:42,235
我是大野

293
00:17:42,877 --> 00:17:44,366
<font color="#ffff54">Tsuda, sir.</font>

294
00:17:43,110 --> 00:17:45,444
我是津田

295
00:17:49,043 --> 00:17:50,907
<font color="#ffff54">What are you doing here?</font>

296
00:17:49,235 --> 00:17:51,319
