321
00:19:01,771 --> 00:19:05,829
<font color="#ffff54">We'll take you to our office, now.</font>

322
00:19:02,069 --> 00:19:03,819
待會先去辦公室

323
00:19:03,861 --> 00:19:06,277
請各位休息一下

324
00:19:06,038 --> 00:19:09,562
<font color="#ffff54">Have some rest and the Boss
will take you out to dinner, later.</font>

325
00:19:06,319 --> 00:19:10,444
