326
00:19:11,803 --> 00:19:13,599
<font color="#ffff54">Hi, my name's Ryoji.</font>

327
00:19:12,361 --> 00:19:14,402
我叫良二

328
00:19:13,903 --> 00:19:17,734
<font color="#ffff54">I have some drinks and ice cream here,
so if you want some, let me know.</font>

329
00:19:14,444 --> 00:19:16,402
車上有飲料跟冰淇淋

330
00:19:16,444 --> 00:19:18,402
請儘管吩咐

331
00:19:18,703 --> 00:19:21,128
<font color="#ffff54">Shiraishi, let's go.</font>

332
00:19:18,944 --> 00:19:21,235
