333
00:19:21,277 --> 00:19:22,694
是

334
00:20:22,832 --> 00:20:24,765
<font color="#ffff54">Want something to drink?</font>

335
00:20:23,194 --> 00:20:24,902
你要喝東西嗎？

336
00:20:26,698 --> 00:20:30,153
<font color="#ffff54">No. My stomach still hurts
from where you stabbed me.</font>

337
00:20:27,027 --> 00:20:30,444
不要，我肚子痛得喝不下

338
00:21:24,661 --> 00:21:26,457
<font color="#ffff54">What luxury, they're spoiling us.</font>

339
00:21:24,944 --> 00:21:27,027
簡直像在作夢啊

340
00:21:30,426 --> 00:21:33,393
<font color="#ffff54">We haven't used
this office for quite a while.</font>

341
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:34,569
這裡廢棄很久了，有點髒

342
00:21:34,293 --> 00:21:38,555
<font color="#ffff54">It's a bit messy, but you won't be staying
here for long, so I guess it's okay.</font>

343
00:21:34,653 --> 00:21:37,069
不過不會待太久

344
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,694
大家隨意就好

345
00:21:38,692 --> 00:21:40,886
<font color="#ffff54">The toilet is over there.</font>

346
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:41,319
