349
00:21:45,191 --> 00:21:45,949
<font color="#ffff54">Okay.</font>

350
00:21:45,402 --> 00:21:45,944
是

351
00:21:47,492 --> 00:21:50,981
<font color="#ffff54">I doubt you'll need these, but in case
you feel lonely, take your pick.</font>

352
00:21:47,860 --> 00:21:49,902
會不會用到不曉得

353
00:21:49,944 --> 00:21:51,486
請大家隨便挑一把

354
00:21:54,025 --> 00:21:57,685
<font color="#ffff54">We conned these out of some Yanks,
so I don't know if they're any good.</font>

355
00:21:54,319 --> 00:21:56,027
這是從老美那裡騙來的

356
00:21:56,069 --> 00:21:57,944
不知道好不好用

357
00:22:03,024 --> 00:22:04,490
<font color="#ffff54">What the fuck's that about?</font>

358
00:22:03,319 --> 00:22:04,985
怎麼回事？

359
00:22:08,690 --> 00:22:10,623
<font color="#ffff54">Just the Anan lot saying "hello".
Often happens.</font>

360
00:22:09,069 --> 00:22:11,528
對方來打聲招呼罷了

361
00:22:11,323 --> 00:22:16,483
<font color="#ffff54">But I'm sure there'll be a truce soon.</font>

362
00:22:11,569 --> 00:22:14,528
這是常有的事

363
00:22:14,569 --> 00:22:16,402
這樣就扯平了吧

364
00:22:24,222 --> 00:22:26,711
<font color="#ffff54">What happens now?</font>

365
00:22:24,777 --> 00:22:27,277
以後會怎麼樣呢？

366
00:22:27,422 --> 00:22:32,582
<font color="#ffff54">Our boss phoned the
Anan clan a little while ago.</font>

367
00:22:27,777 --> 00:22:33,069
我大哥剛才打電話給阿南組了

368
00:22:32,788 --> 00:22:37,982
<font color="#ffff54">Apparently your
arrival's got them a bit excited.</font>

369
00:22:33,319 --> 00:22:35,444
因為你們來助陣

370
00:22:35,486 --> 00:22:38,486
好像刺激到對方了

371
00:22:42,722 --> 00:22:45,553
<font color="#ffff54">How many of you does
it take to put a kettle on?</font>

372
00:22:43,194 --> 00:22:45,569
你們擠在那裡煮開水幹嘛

373
00:22:58,187 --> 00:23:02,279
<font color="#ffff54">Boss, I suppose we ought
to return their greeting.</font>

374
00:22:58,569 --> 00:23:03,111
大哥，我們也去打聲招呼吧

375
00:23:11,019 --> 00:23:12,542
<font color="#ffff54">Here I go.</font>

376
00:23:11,569 --> 00:23:13,027
我去了

377
00:24:23,647 --> 00:24:26,375
<font color="#ffff54">Well that was impressive.</font>

