00:24:24,152 --> 00:24:26,403
連個屁也沒有嘛，渾蛋

379
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:32,413
<font color="#ffff54">The fucking Yank sold me a dud again.</font>

380
00:24:28,902 --> 00:24:32,652
臭老美，又賣些爛貨

381
00:24:34,113 --> 00:24:35,341
<font color="#ffff54">Now what?</font>

382
00:24:34,444 --> 00:24:36,194
現在怎麼辦？

383
00:24:47,279 --> 00:24:51,644
<font color="#ffff54">It all started out with an idiot from
our group shooting an Anan man.</font>

384
00:24:47,777 --> 00:24:49,528
我們家的傻小子

385
00:24:49,569 --> 00:24:52,361
開槍打了對方的人

386
00:24:52,011 --> 00:24:57,273
<font color="#ffff54">It's nothing serious, though.
The other man didn't even die.</font>

387
00:24:52,403 --> 00:24:54,361
所以才搞成這樣

388
00:24:54,403 --> 00:24:56,444
其實沒什麼大不了的

389
00:24:56,486 --> 00:24:58,694
對方也沒死

390
00:24:58,477 --> 00:25:01,535
<font color="#ffff54">So we didn't need any help.</font>

391
00:24:58,735 --> 00:25:02,986
但你們大哥說要來助陣

392
00:25:01,677 --> 00:25:05,110
<font color="#ffff54">But your old man insisted
on sending you across.</font>

393
00:25:03,278 --> 00:25:06,194
