401
00:25:20,509 --> 00:25:27,669
<font color="#ffff54">That's news to me.
Like I said, your old man insisted.</font>

402
00:25:21,111 --> 00:25:24,027
沒這回事吧

403
00:25:24,111 --> 00:25:28,902
