406
00:25:31,181 --> 00:25:33,841
<font color="#ffff54">Just one of those little problems
we encounter every day.</font>

407
00:25:31,652 --> 00:25:34,528
常有的小衝突罷了

408
00:25:34,048 --> 00:25:37,947
<font color="#ffff54">Not an inter-clan thing or anything.</font>

409
00:25:34,610 --> 00:25:38,152
不至於要殺到你死我活啦

410
00:26:39,976 --> 00:26:41,670
<font color="#ffff54">What are your plans for tonight?</font>

411
00:26:40,735 --> 00:26:42,444
你們待會要做什麼？

412
00:26:44,976 --> 00:26:47,841
<font color="#ffff54">Mr. Uechi said he'd take us out.</font>

413
00:26:45,278 --> 00:26:48,319
跟上地先生去鎮上逛逛

414
00:27:15,107 --> 00:27:16,971
<font color="#ffff54">What part of Tokyo are you from?</font>

415
00:27:15,569 --> 00:27:17,569
