419
00:27:23,873 --> 00:27:26,465
<font color="#ffff54">Then you know
Tommy's, by the station?</font>

420
00:27:28,406 --> 00:27:29,838
<font color="#ffff54">Never heard of it.</font>

421
00:27:28,861 --> 00:27:30,735
