422
00:27:33,839 --> 00:27:35,237
<font color="#ffff54">It's quite a well-known joint.</font>

423
00:27:34,194 --> 00:27:35,569
蠻有名的說

424
00:27:35,439 --> 00:27:37,133
<font color="#ffff54">Didn't you hear me?</font>

