00:27:48,472 --> 00:27:49,769
<font color="#ffff54">Smoke?</font>

429
00:27:48,944 --> 00:27:50,527
吸一口嗎？

430
00:27:54,005 --> 00:27:55,199
<font color="#ffff54">What's that?</font>

431
00:27:54,319 --> 00:27:56,111
那是什麼？

432
00:27:56,437 --> 00:27:57,768
<font color="#ffff54">Marijuana.</font>

433
00:27:56,944 --> 00:27:58,861
大麻

434
00:27:59,371 --> 00:28:03,770
<font color="#ffff54">I don't do drugs,
I only do amphetamines.</font>

435
00:27:59,735 --> 00:28:02,278
那是麻藥吧

436
00:28:02,361 --> 00:28:04,361
我只打安非他命

437
00:28:11,636 --> 00:28:15,569
<font color="#ffff54">- Are you feeling okay?
- I'm fine.</font>

438
00:28:12,236 --> 00:28:14,153
