445
00:28:42,652 --> 00:28:45,736
以後集體行動很危險

446
00:28:46,433 --> 00:28:49,797
<font color="#ffff54">And let anyone who wants
to go, go back to Tokyo.</font>

447
00:28:47,153 --> 00:28:50,402
想回東京的人最好讓他們走

448
00:28:52,133 --> 00:28:54,100
<font color="#ffff54">They're not playing games here.</font>

449
00:28:52,527 --> 00:28:54,527
