01:08:52,569 --> 01:08:53,819
你試試

913
01:09:00,817 --> 01:09:03,841
<font color="#ffff54">- I'll tell you when to throw, okay?
- Okay.</font>

914
01:09:01,486 --> 01:09:04,319
我說好才丟喔，知道嗎？

915
01:09:04,150 --> 01:09:06,776
<font color="#ffff54">Aim over here, okay?</font>

916
01:09:04,611 --> 01:09:07,235
這邊喔，往這邊丟喔，開始囉

917
01:09:07,117 --> 01:09:09,879
<font color="#ffff54">Ready? Now!</font>

918
01:09:07,736 --> 01:09:10,694
預備，好

919
01:09:12,650 --> 01:09:14,015
<font color="#ffff54">Shit! No more bullets!</font>

920
01:09:13,027 --> 01:09:14,402
沒子彈了

921
01:09:14,149 --> 01:09:15,877
<font color="#ffff54">You're fucking impressive too!</font>

922
01:09:14,444 --> 01:09:16,819
你還不是打不中，王八蛋

923
01:11:15,340 --> 01:11:18,205
<font color="#ffff54">We'll squeeze
Takahashi until he squeals.</font>

924
01:11:15,860 --> 01:11:18,736
只能把高橋抓起來好好修理了

925
01:11:19,640 --> 01:11:21,970
<font color="#ffff54">The Boss has got
no options left anyway.</font>

926
01:11:20,110 --> 01:11:22,985
大哥也騎虎難下了

927
01:12:34,667 --> 01:12:37,065
<font color="#ffff54">Mr. Uechi., you go in front.</font>

928
01:12:35,152 --> 01:12:38,069
上地先生，麻煩你

929
01:12:51,300 --> 01:12:52,926
<font color="#ffff54">What is it?</font>

930
01:12:51,902 --> 01:12:53,319
什麼事？

931
01:12:56,266 --> 01:12:57,698
<font color="#ffff54">Is Mr. Takahashi there?</font>

932
01:12:56,735 --> 01:12:59,069
高橋先生在嗎？

933
01:12:58,699 --> 01:13:00,325
<font color="#ffff54">My name's Takashi...</font>

934
01:12:59,111 --> 01:13:01,486
我就是高橋

935
01:13:01,999 --> 01:13:03,659
<font color="#ffff54">Must be a mistake.</font>

936
01:13:02,528 --> 01:13:04,528
打擾了

937
01:13:17,697 --> 01:13:20,755
<font color="#ffff54">Should have known he wouldn't
register in his own name.</font>

938
01:13:18,319 --> 01:13:20,277
他不可能用本名投宿

939
01:13:20,403 --> 01:13:22,277
沒錯

940
01:14:32,058 --> 01:14:33,490
<font color="#ffff54">Takahashi.</font>

941
01:14:32,528 --> 01:14:33,528
高橋

942
01:15:45,186 --> 01:15:47,346
<font color="#ffff54">I swear I know nothing.</font>

943
01:15:46,069 --> 01:15:47,986
我真的不知情啦

944
01:15:59,919 --> 01:16:06,216
<font color="#ffff54">Our boss always wanted to
work with the Anan group.</font>

945
01:16:00,569 --> 01:16:07,152
老大想跟阿南組合作啦

946
01:16:07,985 --> 01:16:13,247
<font color="#ffff54">He had to get rid of his
relative Nakamatsu first.</font>

947
01:16:08,694 --> 01:16:12,403
所以中松那個老傢伙會礙事吧

948
01:16:12,444 --> 01:16:14,444
因為我們跟他是結拜兄弟

949
01:16:15,217 --> 01:16:21,173
<font color="#ffff54">The argument
was the perfect excuse...</font>

950
01:16:16,069 --> 01:16:20,319
他想藉這次的衝突

951
01:16:20,361 --> 01:16:27,027
跟阿南組聯手毀了中松

952
01:16:22,550 --> 01:16:26,005
<font color="#ffff54">for him to eliminate Nakamatsu.</font>

953
01:16:26,884 --> 01:16:28,680
<font color="#ffff54">So why expel me?</font>

954
01:16:27,444 --> 01:16:29,819
那為什麼要把我逐出門戶？

955
01:16:29,283 --> 01:16:34,148
<font color="#ffff54">Your patch is doing
great business. He's greedy.</font>

956
01:16:29,861 --> 01:16:31,444
你的地盤油水多

957
01:16:33,444 --> 01:16:35,444
所以他才想要吧

958
01:16:35,083 --> 01:16:36,515
<font color="#ffff54">Listen Murakawa...</font>

959
01:16:35,486 --> 01:16:36,777
我說村川

960
01:16:39,949 --> 01:16:46,906
<font color="#ffff54">The Boss is coming
to Okinawa to see Anan.</font>

961
01:16:40,527 --> 01:16:47,444
老大下次要來這裡找阿南

962
01:16:49,048 --> 01:16:52,344
<font color="#ffff54">You could take over
Nakamatsu's patch.</font>

963
01:16:49,486 --> 01:16:55,069
中松的地盤讓給你怎麼樣？

964
01:16:54,448 --> 01:16:56,608
<font color="#ffff54">I can arrange it.</font>

965
01:16:55,194 --> 01:16:57,735
我可以幫你喬

966
01:17:16,346 --> 01:17:17,869
<font color="#ffff54">You want a go?</font>

967
01:17:16,986 --> 01:17:18,319
你來吧？

968
01:17:20,513 --> 01:17:21,673
<font color="#ffff54">Not that.</font>

969
01:17:20,986 --> 01:17:22,861
不必了

970
01:18:07,209 --> 01:18:09,403
<font color="#ffff54">How do we get back
now you've destroyed our car?</font>

971
01:18:07,819 --> 01:18:09,819
你把車炸了，怎麼回去啊

972
01:18:10,842 --> 01:18:12,331
<font color="#ffff54">Sorry.</font>

973
01:18:11,485 --> 01:18:13,319
對不起

974
01:19:28,970 --> 01:19:30,301
<font color="#ffff54">Who are you?</font>

975
01:19:29,569 --> 01:19:30,360
有什麼事嗎？

976
01:19:34,702 --> 01:19:35,964
<font color="#ffff54">Sorry, I got lost.</font>

977
01:19:35,319 --> 01:19:36,902
我走錯了

978
01:20:44,830 --> 01:20:46,387
<font color="#ffff54">Are you coming back?</font>

979
01:20:45,485 --> 01:20:47,277
你會回來嗎？

980
01:20:49,130 --> 01:20:50,222
<font color="#ffff54">Maybe...</font>

981
01:20:49,694 --> 01:20:51,444
或許吧

982
01:20:52,130 --> 01:20:53,619
<font color="#ffff54">You'll be here?</font>

983
01:20:52,694 --> 01:20:54,360
你會等我嗎？

984
01:20:54,563 --> 01:20:59,519
<font color="#ffff54">Maybe... Can I have a go with it?</font>

985
01:20:55,111 --> 01:20:56,944
或許吧

986
01:20:58,569 --> 01:21:00,028
我可以試試看嗎？

987
01:21:00,069 --> 01:21:02,153
好啊

988
01:21:00,395 --> 01:21:01,327
<font color="#ffff54">Go ahead.</font>

989
01:22:03,491 --> 01:22:05,458
<font color="#ffff54">I'm going with you.</font>

990
01:22:04,194 --> 01:22:06,527
我陪你去吧

991
01:22:06,024 --> 01:22:07,218
<font color="#ffff54">Forget it...</font>

992
01:22:06,569 --> 01:22:08,694
不必啦，渾蛋

993
01:22:12,491 --> 01:22:14,617
<font color="#ffff54">You're going straight soon.</font>

994
01:22:13,235 --> 01:22:15,986
你想從良了吧

995
01:22:18,777 --> 01:22:20,444
是…

996
01:24:39,746 --> 01:24:41,440
<font color="#ffff54">Fuck you.</font>

997
01:24:40,277 --> 01:24:42,152
渾蛋

998
01:24:42,612 --> 01:24:45,477
<font color="#ffff54">In ten minutes, the lights go out.</font>

999
01:24:42,944 --> 01:24:46,694
那麼10分鐘後行動

1000
